onios F.C.|Panionios]]<ref>[http://www.arisfc.gr/index.cfm?pid=2&view=detail&id=877]</ref>\n* 6 July: Midfielder [[Vasilios Rovas]] agrees to join Aris from [[Atromitos F.C.|Atromitos]]<ref>[http://www.arisfc.gr/index.cfm?pid=2&view=detail&id=898]</ref>\n* 7 July: Defender [[Kristi Vangjeli]] agrees to extend for three years his contract with Aris<ref>[http://www.arisfc.gr/index.cfm?pid=2&view=detail&id=905]</ref>\n\n==Current squad==\n{{Fs start}}\n{{Fs player|no=1|nat=Greece|pos=GK|name=[[Michalis Sifakis]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=2|nat=Brazil|pos=DF|name=[[Darcy Dolce Neto]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=3|nat=Argentina|pos=DF|name=[[Carlos Arano]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=4|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=[[Efthimios Kouloucheris]]|other=[[Captain (association football)#Vice-captain|vice-captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=5|nat=Portugal|pos=DF|name=[[Ronaldo Guiaro]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=6|nat=Tunisia|pos=MF|name=[[Mehdi Nafti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=7|nat=Spain|pos=MF|name=[[Toni Calvo]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=8|nat=Bolivia|pos=MF|name=[[Ronald Garc\u00eda Nacho|Nacho Garc\u00eda]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=9|nat=Argentina|pos=MF|name=[[Dario Fernandez]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=10|nat=Spain|pos=FW|name=[[Koke (footballer)|Sergio Koke]] |other=[[Captain (association football)#Club|captain]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=11|nat=USA|pos=FW|name=[[Freddy Adu]]}} (on loan from [[S.L. Benfica|Benfica]])\n{{Fs player|no=12|nat=Brazil|pos=DF|name=[[Marco Aur\u00e9lio Ribeiro Barbieri|Marco Aurelio]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=14|nat=USA|pos=FW|name=[[Eddie Johnson (American soccer)|Eddie Johnson]]}} (on loan from [[Fulham F.C.|Fulham]])\n{{Fs player|no=15|nat=Argentina|pos=DF|name=[[Cristian Nasuti]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=16|nat=Spain|pos=FW|name=[[Felipe Sanch\u00f3n Huerta]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=17|nat=France|pos=MF|name=[[Camel Meriem]]}}\n{{Fs mid}}\n{{Fs player|no=18|nat=Argentina|pos=FW|name=[[Javier C\u00e1mpora]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=20|nat=Spain|pos=MF|name=[[Francisco Javier Peral|Javito]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=22|nat=Greece|pos=DF|name=[[Thomas Graikos]]}}\n