r playing in Greece for 5 years.\n\n{|\n|- style='vertical-align:top'\n||\n'''EU Nationals'''\n*{{Flag icon|ESP}} [[Toni Calvo]]\n*{{Flag icon|ESP}} [[Koke (footballer)|Sergio Koke]]\n*{{Flag icon|ESP}} [[Francisco Javier Peral|Javito]]\n*{{Flag icon|IRE}} [[Ian Daly]]\n*{{Flag icon|FRA}} [[Valentin Roberge]]\n||\n'''EU Nationals (Dual citizenship)'''\n*{{Flag icon|ALB}} {{Flag icon|GRE}} [[Kristi Vangjeli]]\n*{{Flag icon|AUS}} {{Flag icon|GRE}} Sakis Theodoropoulos\n*{{Flag icon|BRA}} {{Flag icon|ITA}} [[Darcy Dolce Neto]]\n*{{Flag icon|BRA}} {{Flag icon|POR}} [[Ronaldo Guiaro]]\n*{{Flag icon|TUN}} {{Flag icon|FRA}} [[Mehdi Nafti]]\n*{{Flag icon|ARG}} {{Flag icon|ESP}} [[Carlos Arano]]\n*{{Flag icon|ARG}} {{Flag icon|ITA}} [[Cristian Nasuti]]\n\n||\n'''Non-EU Nationals'''\n\n*{{Flag icon|BOL}} [[Ronald Garc\u00eda Nacho|Nacho Garc\u00eda]]\n*{{Flag icon|USA}} [[Freddy Adu]]\n*{{Flag icon|USA}} [[Eddie Johnson (American soccer)|Eddie Johnson]]\n*{{Flag icon|ARG}} [[Javier C\u00e1mpora]]\n||\n|}\n\n===International players===\n{|\n|- style='vertical-align:top'\n||\n*{{Flag icon|GRE}} [[Michalis Sifakis]]\n*{{Flag icon|GRE}} [[Athanassios Prittas]]\n*{{Flag icon|GRE}} [[Christos Aravidis]]\n*{{Flag icon|AUS}} Sakis Theodoropoulos\n*{{Flag icon|BRA}} [[Ronaldo Guiaro]]\n*{{Flag icon|USA}} [[Freddy Adu]]\n||\n*{{Flag icon|USA}} [[Eddie Johnson (American soccer)|Eddie Johnson]]\n*{{Flag icon|BOL}} [[Ronald Garc\u00eda Nacho|Nacho Garc\u00eda]]\n*{{Flag icon|TUN}} [[Mehdi Nafti]]\n*{{Flag icon|ESP}} [[Toni Calvo]]\n*{{Flag icon|ESP}} [[Francisco Javier Peral|Javito]]\n*{{Flag icon|IRL}} [[Ian Daly]]\n||\n|}\n\n===Squad changes===\n'''In:'''\n{{fb in2 header}}\n\n{{fb in2 player |tc=GRE  |bg= |p=[[Leandro Graci\u00e1n|Graci\u00e1n]] |type=Loan |eu=n |nb=ARG |n=11 |pos=MF |age={{Age|1982|8|6|2009|6|14}}|fcl=[[Boca Juniors]] {{flagicon|ARG}} |w=S |e=2010 |f=$250K |os= [https://web.archive.org/web/20110719143552/http://www.arisfc.gr/index.cfm?pid=2&view=detail&id=823 arisfc.g